    "Another student noted, \"While ChatGPT is helpful, it shouldn't be our only source.",
    "We need to continue developing our research skills.",
    "\"Additionally, there are concerns regarding the ethical use of ChatGPT and its limitations.",
    "A student remarked, \"I think we need clear guidelines on how to use Chat-GPT ethically, especially in academic settings.\"",
    "Another participant pointed out, \"Understanding the limitations of ChatGPT is important; it can't replace the depths of knowledge we gain from traditional learning methods.\""
